---
import SiteLayout from '../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "QR Code Generator",
  "url": "https://siliconbased.dev/qr-generator",
  "description": "Generate QR codes for URLs, text, WiFi credentials, vCards, and email. Customize size, colors, and error correction level. Download as PNG or SVG.",
  "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any",
  "offers": {
    "@type": "Offer",
    "price": "0",
    "priceCurrency": "USD"
  },
  "author": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "GAB Ventures",
    "url": "https://gab.ae"
  }
};

const htmlBody = `<div class="page-content">
<div class="hero">
  <h1>QR Code Generator</h1>
  <p>Generate customizable QR codes for URLs, text, WiFi, and more. Instantly download as PNG or SVG.</p>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <div class="tabs" id="typeTabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" data-type="url">URL</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-type="text">Text</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-type="wifi">WiFi</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-type="vcard">vCard</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-type="email">Email</button>
  </div>

  <div class="content-grid">
    <div class="left-col" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-header">
          <h3 id="formTitle">Enter URL</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-body" id="formContainer">
          <!-- Dynamic Form Content injected here -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-header">
          <h3>Customization</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-body">
          <div class="settings-group">
            <div class="setting-row">
              <span class="setting-label">Foreground Color</span>
              <div class="color-picker-wrap">
                <input type="color" id="colorDark" class="color-input" value="#000000">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="setting-row">
              <span class="setting-label">Background Color</span>
              <div class="color-picker-wrap">
                <input type="color" id="colorLight" class="color-input" value="#ffffff">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="setting-row">
              <span class="setting-label">Error Correction</span>
              <select id="eccLevel" class="select-field">
                <option value="L">Low (7%)</option>
                <option value="M" selected>Medium (15%)</option>
                <option value="Q">Quartile (25%)</option>
                <option value="H">High (30%)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="setting-row">
              <span class="setting-label">Padding (Modules)</span>
              <select id="paddingSize" class="select-field">
                <option value="0">0</option>
                <option value="1">1</option>
                <option value="2">2</option>
                <option value="4" selected>4</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="right-col preview-card">
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-header">
          <h3>Preview</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-body" style="padding: 16px;">
          <div class="qr-container" id="qrContainer">
            <!-- QR code rendered here -->
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnDownloadPng" style="flex: 1;">Download PNG</button>
            <button class="btn" id="btnDownloadSvg" style="flex: 1;">Download SVG</button>
            <button class="btn" id="btnCopyImg" style="flex: 1; min-width: 100%;">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"></path></svg>
              Copy Image
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="seo-content">
    <h2>What is a QR Code?</h2>
    <p>A QR (Quick Response) code is a type of two-dimensional matrix barcode invented in 1994. It consists of black squares arranged in a square grid on a white background, which can be read by an imaging device such as a smartphone camera. QR codes can store significantly more data than standard barcodes, including URLs, text, contact information, and WiFi credentials.</p>

    <h2>How Error Correction Works</h2>
    <p>QR codes use Reed-Solomon error correction to ensure the code remains scannable even if it's partially damaged, obscured, or customized with a logo. There are four levels of error correction:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Low (L)</strong>: Can recover up to 7% of data. Ideal for clean, digital displays where size must be kept small.</li>
      <li><strong>Medium (M)</strong>: Can recover up to 15% of data. The standard choice for most general purposes.</li>
      <li><strong>Quartile (Q)</strong>: Can recover up to 25% of data. Good for print materials in uncontrolled environments.</li>
      <li><strong>High (H)</strong>: Can recover up to 30% of data. Best for adding logos to the center of the QR code or for harsh industrial environments.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tips for Creating the Best QR Codes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contrast is key:</strong> Always ensure there is a high contrast between the foreground (dots) and the background. Dark dots on a light background work best for scanners.</li>
      <li><strong>Quiet zone:</strong> Leave a sufficient margin (padding) around the QR code. The standard is 4 modules (blocks) to help scanners isolate the code from its surroundings.</li>
      <li><strong>Test before printing:</strong> Always scan your generated QR code with multiple devices before putting it on physical materials like business cards or posters.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Privacy and Security</h2>
    <p>Our QR code generator operates entirely on the client side (in your web browser). The data you enter to generate the code—whether it's a URL, personal vCard details, or WiFi passwords—is never sent to a server. You can even use this tool offline after the page has loaded.</p>
  </div>

</div>

    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="vcardPhone">Phone</label>
      <input type="tel" id="vcardPhone" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="+1 234 567 8900">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="vcardEmail">Email</label>
      <input type="email" id="vcardEmail" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="jane@example.com">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="vcardOrg">Company / Organization</label>
      <input type="text" id="vcardOrg" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="Acme Corp">
    </div>
  \`,
  email: \`
    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="emailTo">Email Address</label>
      <input type="email" id="emailTo" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="hello@example.com">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="emailSubj">Subject</label>
      <input type="text" id="emailSubj" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="Hello there">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="emailBody">Message</label>
      <textarea id="emailBody" class="input-field qr-input" placeholder="Type your message..."></textarea>
    </div>
  \`
};

const titles = {
  url: 'Enter URL',
  text: 'Enter Text',
  wifi: 'WiFi Credentials',
  vcard: 'Contact Info (vCard)',
  email: 'Email Draft'
};

let currentType = 'url';

function initForms() {
  formContainer.innerHTML = forms[currentType];
  formTitle.textContent = titles[currentType];
}

tabBtns.forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    tabBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
    btn.classList.add('active');
    currentType = btn.getAttribute('data-type');
    initForms();
  });
});

const qrContainer = document.getElementById('qrContainer');
const colorDark = document.getElementById('colorDark');
const colorLight = document.getElementById('colorLight');
const eccLevel = document.getElementById('eccLevel');
const paddingSize = document.getElementById('paddingSize');
const btnDownloadPng = document.getElementById('btnDownloadPng');
const btnDownloadSvg = document.getElementById('btnDownloadSvg');
const btnCopyImg = document.getElementById('btnCopyImg');

let currentQrText = '';

function generatePayload() {
  switch (currentType) {
    case 'url':
      return document.getElementById('inputUrl')?.value.trim() || '';
    case 'text':
      return document.getElementById('inputText')?.value || '';
    case 'wifi':
      // Escape semicolons and colons which break WIFI format
      const ssid = (document.getElementById('wifiSsid')?.value.trim() || '').replace(/([\\\\;,:])/g, '\\\\$1');
      const pass = (document.getElementById('wifiPass')?.value || '').replace(/([\\\\;,:])/g, '\\\\$1');
      const type = document.getElementById('wifiType')?.value;
      const hidden = document.getElementById('wifiHidden')?.checked ? 'H:true' : '';
      if (!ssid) return '';
      return "WIFI:S:" + ssid + ";T:" + type + ";P:" + pass + ";" + hidden + ";;";
    case 'vcard':
      const fName = document.getElementById('vcardFirst')?.value.trim() || '';
      const lName = document.getElementById('vcardLast')?.value.trim() || '';
      const phone = document.getElementById('vcardPhone')?.value.trim() || '';
      const email = document.getElementById('vcardEmail')?.value.trim() || '';
      const org = document.getElementById('vcardOrg')?.value.trim() || '';
      if (!fName && !lName && !phone && !email) return '';
      return "BEGIN:VCARD\\nVERSION:3.0\\nN:" + lName + ";" + fName + ";;;\\nFN:" + fName + " " + lName + "\\nORG:" + org + "\\nTEL:" + phone + "\\nEMAIL:" + email + "\\nEND:VCARD";
    case 'email':
      const to = document.getElementById('emailTo')?.value.trim() || '';
      // Escape semicolons and colons which break MATMSG
      const subj = (document.getElementById('emailSubj')?.value.trim() || '').replace(/;/g, '').replace(/:/g, '');
      const body = (document.getElementById('emailBody')?.value || '').replace(/;/g, '').replace(/:/g, '');
      if (!to) return '';
      return "MATMSG:TO:" + to + ";SUB:" + subj + ";BODY:" + body + ";;";
    default:
      return '';
  }
}

function getEcc() {
  const val = eccLevel.value;
  if (val === 'L') return qrcodegen.QrCode.Ecc.LOW;
  if (val === 'M') return qrcodegen.QrCode.Ecc.MEDIUM;
  if (val === 'Q') return qrcodegen.QrCode.Ecc.QUARTILE;
  return qrcodegen.QrCode.Ecc.HIGH;
}

function renderQr() {
  currentQrText = generatePayload();
  qrContainer.innerHTML = '';

  if (!currentQrText) {
    qrContainer.innerHTML = '<span style="color:#888;font-size:0.9rem;">Enter data to generate QR code</span>';
    btnDownloadPng.disabled = true;
    btnDownloadSvg.disabled = true;
    return;
  }

  try {
    const qr = qrcodegen.QrCode.encodeText(currentQrText, getEcc());
    const pad = parseInt(paddingSize.value, 10);
    const dark = colorDark.value;
    const light = colorLight.value;

    const size = qr.size + pad * 2;
    const parts = [];
    for (let y = 0; y < qr.size; y++) {
      for (let x = 0; x < qr.size; x++) {
        if (qr.isDark(x, y)) {
          parts.push("M" + (x + pad) + "," + (y + pad) + "h1v1h-1z");
        }
      }
    }

    const svg = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', 'svg');
    svg.setAttribute('viewBox', "0 0 " + size + " " + size);
    svg.setAttribute('stroke', 'none');

    // Background
    const bg = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', 'rect');
    bg.setAttribute('width', '100%');
    bg.setAttribute('height', '100%');
    bg.setAttribute('fill', light);
    svg.appendChild(bg);

    // QR Data
    const path = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', 'path');
    path.setAttribute('d', parts.join(' '));
    path.setAttribute('fill', dark);
    svg.appendChild(path);

    qrContainer.appendChild(svg);
    btnDownloadPng.disabled = false;
    btnDownloadSvg.disabled = false;
    btnCopyImg.disabled = false;
  } catch (err) {
    console.error(err);
    qrContainer.innerHTML = '<span style="color:#ef4444;font-size:0.9rem;">Error generating QR code (data too long?)</span>';
    btnDownloadPng.disabled = true;
    btnDownloadSvg.disabled = true;
    btnCopyImg.disabled = true;
  }
}

function attachInputListeners() {
  const inputs = formContainer.querySelectorAll('.qr-input');
  inputs.forEach(input => {
    input.addEventListener('input', renderQr);
    input.addEventListener('change', renderQr);
  });
}

// Initialize first form
function initForms() {
  formContainer.innerHTML = forms[currentType];
  formTitle.textContent = titles[currentType];
  attachInputListeners();
  renderQr();
}

initForms();

// Settings Listeners
colorDark.addEventListener('input', renderQr);
colorLight.addEventListener('input', renderQr);
eccLevel.addEventListener('change', renderQr);
paddingSize.addEventListener('change', renderQr);

// Image Generation helper
function createQrCanvas(callback) {
  const svg = qrContainer.querySelector('svg');
  if (!svg) return;

  const canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
  // High resolution for PNG download
  const size = 1000;
  canvas.width = size;
  canvas.height = size;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');

  const data = new XMLSerializer().serializeToString(svg);
  const img = new Image();
  const blob = new Blob([data], { type: 'image/svg+xml' });
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);

  img.onload = () => {
    ctx.drawImage(img, 0, 0, size, size);
    URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
    canvas.toBlob((pngBlob) => {
      callback(pngBlob);
    }, 'image/png');
  };
  img.src = url;
}

btnCopyImg.addEventListener('click', async () => {
  try {
    createQrCanvas(async (blob) => {
      if (!blob) return;
      try {
        const item = new ClipboardItem({ 'image/png': blob });
        await navigator.clipboard.write([item]);
        const originalText = btnCopyImg.innerHTML;
        btnCopyImg.innerHTML = '<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> Copied!';
        btnCopyImg.style.borderColor = '#4ade80';
        btnCopyImg.style.color = '#4ade80';
        setTimeout(() => {
          btnCopyImg.innerHTML = originalText;
          btnCopyImg.style.borderColor = '';
          btnCopyImg.style.color = '';
        }, 2000);
      } catch (err) {
        console.error('Failed to copy: ', err);
        alert('Copy to clipboard failed. Your browser might not support this feature.');
      }
    });
  } catch (err) {
    console.error(err);
  }
});

// Downloads
btnDownloadSvg.addEventListener('click', () => {
  const svg = qrContainer.querySelector('svg');
  if (!svg) return;
  const data = new XMLSerializer().serializeToString(svg);
  const blob = new Blob([data], { type: 'image/svg+xml' });
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  const a = document.createElement('a');
  a.href = url;
  a.download = "qrcode-" + currentType + ".svg";
  document.body.appendChild(a);
  a.click();
  document.body.removeChild(a);
  URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
});

btnDownloadPng.addEventListener('click', () => {
  createQrCanvas((pngBlob) => {
    if (!pngBlob) return;
    const pngUrl = URL.createObjectURL(pngBlob);
    const a = document.createElement('a');
    a.href = pngUrl;
    a.download = "qrcode-" + currentType + ".png";
    document.body.appendChild(a);
    a.click();
    document.body.removeChild(a);
    URL.revokeObjectURL(pngUrl);
  });
});

/* --- QR Code Generator Library (Minified qrcodegen by Nayuki) --- */
</script>
</div>`
---

<SiteLayout
  site="siliconbased"
  title="QR Code Generator | Free Online Tool"
  description="Generate QR codes for URLs, text, WiFi credentials, vCards, and email. Customize size, colors, and error correction level. Download as PNG or SVG."
  canonical="https://siliconbased.dev/qr-generator"
  schema={schema}
>
  <Fragment set:html={htmlBody} />

  <style is:inline>

.page-content { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #0a0b10; color: #e0e0e0; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
code, pre, .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

.hero { text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px 16px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f1729 0%, #0a0b10 100%); }
.hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.hero h1 span { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #818cf8, #c084fc); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
.hero p { color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; }

.main { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 20px 80px; flex: 1; width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }

.content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 24px; align-items: start; }

/* Tabs */
.tabs { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.tab-btn { background: #1e2030; border: 1px solid #2a2d40; color: #888; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s; }
.tab-btn:hover { background: #2a2d40; color: #ccc; }
.tab-btn.active { background: #818cf8; color: #fff; border-color: #818cf8; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.2); }

/* Card */
.tool-card { background: #111318; border: 1px solid #1e2030; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
.tool-header { padding: 16px 24px; background: #13151d; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2030; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;}
.tool-header h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ccc; }
.tool-body { padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }

/* Inputs */
.input-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
.input-group label { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #818cf8; }
.input-field { width: 100%; background: #0a0b10; border: 1px solid #1e2030; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.95rem; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
.input-field:focus { border-color: #818cf8; }
.input-field::placeholder { color: #444; }
textarea.input-field { min-height: 120px; resize: vertical; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

/* Form Grids */
.form-grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }

/* Settings Card */
.settings-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
.setting-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.setting-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #ccc; font-weight: 500; }
.color-picker-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.color-input { width: 40px; height: 40px; border: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; background: none; padding: 0; }
.color-input::-webkit-color-swatch-wrapper { padding: 0; }
.color-input::-webkit-color-swatch { border: 1px solid #1e2030; border-radius: 8px; }
.select-field { background: #0a0b10; border: 1px solid #1e2030; color: #e0e0e0; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; outline: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; cursor: pointer; }

/* Preview Card */
.preview-card { position: sticky; top: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.qr-container { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 250px; border: 1px solid #1e2030; }
.qr-container svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; max-width: 250px; }
.qr-container canvas { display: none; }

/* Actions */
.btn { background: #1e2030; border: 1px solid #2a2d40; color: #ccc; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; width: 100%; }
.btn:hover { background: #2a2d40; color: #fff; }
.btn-primary { background: #818cf8; color: #fff; border-color: #818cf8; }
.btn-primary:hover { background: #6366f1; border-color: #6366f1; }

/* SEO Content */
.seo-content { margin-top: 48px; border-top: 1px solid #1e2030; padding-top: 48px; color: #b0b8d0; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
.seo-content h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 16px; }
.seo-content h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.seo-content h3 { color: #e0e0e0; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 24px 0 12px; }
.seo-content p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.seo-content ul { margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 24px; }
.seo-content li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
.seo-content code { background: #111318; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #818cf8; font-size: 0.85em; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

/* Footer */
.footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px 24px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #555; border-top: 1px solid #151520; margin-top: auto; }
.footer a { color: #818cf8; text-decoration: none; }
.footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* Responsive - Mobile First */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .preview-card { position: static; order: -1; }
  .tabs { justify-content: center; }
}

</style>
</SiteLayout>
